data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION TO BE COMPLETED BEFORE END OF JULY! The expanded Andrew II floorplan is the perfect home for a first-time buyer or a buyer looking to upgrade into a larger home! Just over 2,000 sq. ft. this home fits everything you need at an affordable price AND it comes with a two-year builder warranty! The first floor includes a separate living room, dining room, and kitchen. Open layout between the kitchen, featuring upgraded cabinets and granite countertops, and the breakfast area. Just off the kitchen are the first floor laundry room and powder room with easy access to your two-car garage with keyless entry Upstairs includes a large master bedroom with a master bathroom and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms also include walk-in closets and a spare guest room for even more room! There is still time to make this home unique to you!
